FaveCon AddressBook Changelog
=============================


	0.1.3 -> 0.1.5
--------------------
 * easier system for future translations
 * fixed utf8 bug
 * fixed PHP magic_quotes bug
 * calendar for date of birth has no restrictions
 * added possibility to reload contact list manually
 * improved view of contact details
 * backup & recovery:
   - CSV
   - XML & XML Export for personal purposes
 * minor bugfixes


	0.1.2 -> 0.1.3
--------------------
 * added possibility to (de)activate user
 * added option to add a short comment for each user


	0.1.1 -> 0.1.2
--------------------
 * Google Maps loading correctly!

 
	0.1 -> 0.1.1
--------------------
 * Translation failure fixed: "PLZ" is "Postal code" in English
 * Error while searching for "title" of a contact
 * While searching sometimes a curious string appears as a founded contact
